    >
  </section>

  <section id="retention">
    <h2>6. Data retention</h2>
    <p>
      We keep waitlist emails until the relevant platform launches and you have
      been notified, or until you ask us to remove you. Purchase records are
      retained as required for tax and accounting purposes.
    </p>
    <span class="todo">Set concrete retention periods per data type and legal requirements.</span>
